<body>
    <h1>FAQs</h1>
    <section>
        <h4>
            Q: What is the purpose of the grocery section on your e-commerce website?
        </h4>
        <p>
            A: Our grocery section is designed to provide a convenient online platform for customers to browse, select, and purchase a wide range of grocery items from the comfort of their homes.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>
            Q: How do I place an order for groceries on your website?
        </h4>
        <p>
            A: To place a grocery order, simply navigate to the "Groceries" section, browse through the categories or use the search bar to find specific items, add them to your cart, and proceed to checkout.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>
            Q: What payment methods are accepted for grocery purchases?
        </h4>
        <p>
            A: We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards, digital wallets, and other secure online payment options. You can choose the method that suits you best during the checkout process.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>
            Q: Can I schedule a delivery for my grocery order?
        </h4>
        <p>
            A: Yes, you can schedule the delivery of your grocery order at a time that is convenient for you. During the checkout process, you'll have the option to choose a delivery time slot based on availability in your area.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>
            Q: Is there a minimum order amount for grocery delivery?
        </h4>
        <p>
            A: The minimum order amount for grocery delivery may vary depending on your location. You can check the specific details during the checkout process, and any applicable fees or minimum order requirements will be clearly communicated.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>Q: How are the groceries packaged for delivery?</h4>
        <p>
            A: We take great care in packaging your groceries to ensure they reach you in the best condition. Items are carefully packed to prevent damage, and we use eco-friendly packaging whenever possible.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>Q: Can I modify or cancel my grocery order after placing it?</h4>
        <p>
            A: Once an order is confirmed, modifications may be limited. However, you can contact our customer support for assistance. Cancellation policies are also available on our website.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>Q: What do I do if I receive damaged or incorrect items in my grocery order?</h4>
        <p>
            A: If you encounter any issues with your grocery order, please contact our customer support immediately. We will work to resolve the issue and ensure you receive the correct items in the best condition possible.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4>Q: Are there any delivery charges for grocery orders?</h4>
        <p>
            A: Delivery charges may apply based on your location and the delivery option chosen. You can view the delivery charges during the checkout process before confirming your order.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: Can I return perishable items if they are not up to my satisfaction?</h4>
        <p>
            A: Yes, you can return perishable items if they do not meet your satisfaction. Please contact our customer support within a specified timeframe, and we will assist you with the return process.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: How do you ensure the freshness of perishable items during delivery?</h4>
        <p>
            A: We have dedicated processes in place to maintain the freshness of perishable items during delivery. Our delivery vehicles are equipped with temperature-controlled storage, and our team takes extra care to handle such items with caution.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: What measures do you take to ensure the safety of the products during the COVID- pandemic?</h4>
        <p>
            A: We prioritize the safety of our customers and staff. Our team follows strict hygiene protocols, and we have implemented contactless delivery options. Additionally, we regularly update our practices to align with the latest health and safety guidelines.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: Can I order groceries for someone else, such as a friend or family member?</h4>
        <p>
            A: Yes, you can place an order for groceries and have them delivered to a different address. During the checkout process, you can specify the delivery address, and you also have the option to include a personalized message or special instructions.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: Are nutritional details and expiration dates provided for the grocery items?</h4>
        <p>
            A: Yes, we strive to provide detailed product information, including nutritional details and expiration dates, for all grocery items. You can find this information on the product pages on our website.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: Do you source organic or locally produced groceries?</h4>
        <p>
            A: We offer a variety of products, including organic and locally sourced groceries. You can use filters on our website to specifically search for these products and make sustainable and conscious choices.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h4>Q: What happens if I miss the scheduled delivery of my grocery order?</h4>
        <p>
            A: If you miss the scheduled delivery, our customer support team will reach out to reschedule. In case of repeated missed deliveries, additional charges may apply, and we recommend contacting us to make alternative arrangements.
        </p>
    </section>
